{"tid":1635800,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘101","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:25:53.000Z","uid":79108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"929544787b1f5cd95f3486d67580daf6ab94a499","tid":1635800,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"跳閘本身會犯港鐵付例， 大家真係唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跳閘雖然極低風險<br />\n但好多和理都未突破到心理關口 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果有人諗到方法， 例如<br />\n每個站set一個集合點，俾佢知道都吹你唔帳<br />\n每逢00， 15， 30， 45，<br />\n集到20人， 就搵5個做先頭， 煩9d 職員<br />\n可以拍完之後跳 ，或者拍完入去問9佢問題<br />\n其餘人呢個時侯跳 ， 就算俾佢地睇到 想搞你，一黎俾其它人煩緊，2黎如果真係過到黎，20個人一起哄，最圍d人實埋黎。<br />\n真係好似易跳左好多，大家唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果有d平時自己跳開既去帶下d新手, 一定進步神速。所以大家唔好咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba86ff66e501919e275e03b8799cbe298224eefc","tid":1635800,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家唔好搞交通燈喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整爛交通燈只會令到交通擠塞<br />\n迫大家落去搭黨鐵咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c591e8250f62f0d49d506b455338695f0fa2c4ee","tid":1635800,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"推一"},{"pid":"fe04704ed0597fde745b1175530922ffe3ccbf80","tid":1635800,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"唔跳喇, 拎膠水有窿封窿"},{"pid":"f4f04eadb65efc718c370dedf475845758ce2543","tid":1635800,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"訓左成個月？"},{"pid":"78d71d3fc907bca46b8f39ce7963ae5bf5b5c77d","tid":1635800,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4f04eadb65efc718c370dedf475845758ce2543","tid":1635800,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci